Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Those who've laid eyes on\Na Gundam shall not live."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,THERE'S A GUNDAM DOWN HERE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to reload\Nthe explosives for Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop worrying about that\Nright now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Start thinking about what\Nyour next move will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're above the Filchner\NIce Shelf of the Weddell Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be at the Barclay\NBase in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Any signs of enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing on the radar\Nor heat sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll expect Acht's search party\Nto regroup before attacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...rather than assume they've\Ngiven up pursuing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So OZ has one able officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought Heero Yuy and\NTrowa Barton, as requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Zechs Merquise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposed to shake hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero Yuy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The same name as the leader\Nwho held the colonies together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you using your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose there's no point\Nusing names from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've prepared a friendly\Nreception for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to make yourselves\Nat home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zechs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The repairs to Zero One have\Nbeen completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The only things left are\Nthe operational adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Meiser, in charge of\Nrestoring your Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is adjusting\Nthe cockpit to suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Meiser's young, but\Nhis skills are top class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When can we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How about tomorrow morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero Yuy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna say\Nsomething to Colonel Zechs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll thank him,\Nbut in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I'll show\Nmy gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To the soldiers fighting\Nto protect the colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...this battle's merely an\Nobstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm a mere stepping stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never shaken hands\Nwith anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that I can't let\Neither of them die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not Zechs;\Nbut not Heero either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you many times,\Nwe've destroyed Gundam Zero One.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a single stabilizer\Nleft here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait until after I meet\NColonel Zechs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...to decide if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Colonel isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me meet Lieutenant\NNoin, who was in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll meet me if you\Ntell her I'm Relena Peacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But as I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relena 's on her way here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even the Peacecrafts have{\i0}\N{\i1}caught on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I expect Romefeller's found{\i0}\N{\i1}out by now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please be very cautious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, many people\Nwill probably try...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...sucking up to the\NRomefeller Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeating Zechs, who's seen\Nas a Gundam defender...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...would prove one's\Nloyalty to the Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The search party's manhunt\Ncould be intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But Zechs is practically\NOZ's hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they be after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the path Zechs is\Nabout to take wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't mean to eavesdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have at least\Na partial answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,During my many years\Nwith OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...I developed an aesthetic\Nsense in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it's a spirit that\Nfighters could acknowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...in each other, even\Nbetween enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But those Gundam pilots\Nare desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll battle even if it costs\Ntheir lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They live the true lives\Nof soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm much too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They know they're fighting\Nfor the colonies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs, you have someone\Nto protect too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right\Nto protect anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd say that the very\Nthought itself makes me weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:07:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to bring\Nany pride into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm only capable of\Nthat kind of battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll simply be defeated\Nhere by the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Some lessons can only be\Nlearned by risking one's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Noin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle will take awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can fight without\Nany interruptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prevent the search party\Nfrom interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more concerned about\Nthe dignitary of the Peacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Imperial Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important person\Nto you is Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll fight your best knowing\Nyou must protect that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He just doesn't want anyone\Ntouching his mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The self-detonation device\Nisn't connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zechs says you\Nwon't be needing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So Zechs had regrets after\Ntheir last showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This time he really\Nwants to fight it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna fight\Nin your own mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna use yours after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This generosity is blurring\Nthe focus on fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't be an\Nissue with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So he'll fight with Zero Three\Nrather than Zero One.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world could\Nthey be thinking of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees our gift as\Nsome kind of charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But my feelings are unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we restore the\Nleft arm of the Tallgeese?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still time to take\Nthe supply parts off Zero One.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a continuation\Nof our last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tallgeese had its left arm\Ndamaged there, in Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a valid handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's the difference\Nbetween engineers and pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Backstage crew like us\Ndon't feel that kind of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to rid\Nmyself of the weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,2:32 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This weight will be tough\Nfor his left arm to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it begun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my radar out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's below!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's using snow clouds\Nto mask the heat source.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't die in such\Na low-caliber fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost three hours since\Nthe battle started!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a long time for\Na meaningless battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, meaningless?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno the details, but OZ\Nis after you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of two sides\Nwith a mutual enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...fighting against each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Think it's the pilots' fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You might have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But they've been out to kill\Neach other until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So naturally they feel\Nit's some kind of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle will go on until\Nthey realize it is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are people trying to stop time\Nin order to find themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemies are necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the soldier's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier's rejuvenated when\Nhe finds someone to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes that takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now we've lost sight\Nof how to protect the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We really can't afford to\Nbe wasting time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prevent any interruptions,\Nso they can get this over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the search party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa, how will you fight them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have Heero return my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you run out of bullets,{\i0}\N{\i1}click that switch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll make the left arm lighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're right out\Nof fire power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A beam saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa went out of\Nhis way for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no regrets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what happens in war.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wrong turn in the past{\i0}\N{\i1}can be painful for anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you people are still young!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope you'll think about{\i0}\N{\i1}building a new future!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our family is honored{\i0}\N{\i1}to have met with you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Civilian aircraft, land at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a strategic air zone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Pagan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're surveillance suits\Nfrom the search party...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...chasing Zechs Merquise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what they'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't follow us\Nto the Barclay Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The civilian aircraft is{\i0}\N{\i1}accelerating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shoot it down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fighting just up ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stopping his fight\Nwith Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The search party's becoming\Nmore aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His left arm's not working well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave yourself a handicap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being way too kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to rid myself of such\Nsilly pride in this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Relena?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, I've got a letter\Nto deliver to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're in the way!{\i0}\N{\i1}Get lost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This letter explains how\Nyou should live your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're obliged to read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs Merquise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please leave at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must take revenge for{\i0}\N{\i1}the death of my men!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby order you under\Nthe Peacecraft family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this battle immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become strong, Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fitting, for a Peacecraft\Ndaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself how dirty\Nand foul battles really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a true warrior\Nand a Peacecraft knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...you couldn't possibly\Nuse such foul play!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena, call from\NLieutenant Noin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Noin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I misunderstood you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you just sit by\Nand watch this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is neither a duel\Nnor a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just killing each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Precisely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I deserve your contempt,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I can't help myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believe in Colonel Zechs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not about to interrupt{\i0}\N{\i1}any of his plans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat Zechs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone associated with\Na foul group like OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...is an embarrassment to\Nthe Sanc Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Relena!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact that he's\Nassociated with OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't deny that some\Nmistakes were made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't explain it away with his\Nlove for the Sanc Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Relena, no matter what\Nfate has dealt you in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...please don't ever wish\Nfor your brother's death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...he's my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the Peacecraft monarchy\Nfell to the Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...he's had his heart set\Non revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Assembling power in the ruined\NSanc Kingdom was hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He chose to join OZ, to get\Ncloser to the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He waited, donning a disguise\Nhe called Zechs Merquise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My hands have been stained{\i0}\N{\i1}with too much blood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relena is the appropriate person{\i0}\N{\i1}to revive the Sanc Kingdom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Once OZ brought a new wave\Nof chaos to the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...Zechs must've lost a sense\Nof purpose in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He can find the soldier\Nin himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...only when he fights\Nthe Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero lives by his own rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And Zechs wants to battle\Nhim on a level playing field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To embrace the Sanc Kingdom\Nand the Peacecraft name!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's even prepared to\Nlose his life for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll keep believing in him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to stay by his side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter what he does or{\i0}\N{\i1}searches for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fond of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please watch over my brother{\i0}\N{\i1}forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zechs can be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the Peacecraft blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Numerous carriers approaching\Nfrom 3 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably from the search party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Over thirty, but that's only\Na portion of their fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get all the mobile suits ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll attack the search party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you read me, Heero{\i0}\N{\i1}and Zechs?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thirty suits in flight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hundred if they unload{\i0}\N{\i1}all Aries suits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of us should be able\Nto handle thirty easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll attract them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory to the colonies!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll meet again,{\i0}\N{\i1}to continue our battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll be one tough guy{\i0}\N{\i1}to fight from now on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Colonel Zechs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aries troops are ready{\i0}\N{\i1}to be deployed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take Relena with you\Nand make your escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zechs!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I know you've gotten\Naway safely, I'll surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'm gonna fight too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Noin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect the promising\Nleader of the Sanc Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,0:21:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Zechs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad that battle's\Nfinally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The war zone expands\Ninto outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ moves to finally finish off\Nthe Alliance Military.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It also plans to reconcile\Nthe colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Quatre and Duo head\Nfor outer space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...to warn the colonies\Nof OZ's conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But the colonies that had\Nbeen their home...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...declare the Gundams\Nto be their enemies.
